<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q4_v3" title="Q4_v3" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En una receta, se indica que la tercera parte de la cantidad total de azúcar necesaria corresponde a 0,12 kg.</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>¿Cuántos kilogramos de azúcar se necesitan en total para la receta si la tercera parte de esa cantidad es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> del total y corresponde a 0,12 kg?</qti-prompt>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>0,12</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> del total es <m:math><m:mn>0,12</m:mn></m:math> kg, entonces el total debe ser <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>0,12</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,36</m:mn></m:math> kg. Además, la tercera parte de <m:math><m:mn>0,12</m:mn></m:math> es <m:math><m:mn>0,12</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,04</m:mn></m:math> kg, no <m:math><m:mn>0,12</m:mn></m:math> kg.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>0,36</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si la tercera parte del total corresponde a <m:math><m:mn>0,12</m:mn></m:math> kg, entonces el total es <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>0,12</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,36</m:mn></m:math> kg. Verificación: <m:math><m:mn>0,36</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,12</m:mn></m:math> kg.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>0,04</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si el total fuera <m:math><m:mn>0,04</m:mn></m:math> kg, su tercera parte sería <m:math><m:mn>0,04</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,0133</m:mn></m:math> kg aproximadamente, y no <m:math><m:mn>0,12</m:mn></m:math> kg. El total correcto se obtiene multiplicando por <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math>: <m:math><m:mn>0,12</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,36</m:mn></m:math> kg.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>0,24</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si el total fuera <m:math><m:mn>0,24</m:mn></m:math> kg, entonces su tercera parte sería <m:math><m:mn>0,24</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,08</m:mn></m:math> kg, no <m:math><m:mn>0,12</m:mn></m:math> kg. Como <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> del total es <m:math><m:mn>0,12</m:mn></m:math> kg, el total correcto es <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>0,12</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,36</m:mn></m:math> kg.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la información dada</strong></p>
            <p>El enunciado dice que la tercera parte de la cantidad total de azúcar es <m:math><m:mn>0,12</m:mn></m:math> kg.</p>
            <p>Esto significa que:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo> </m:mo><m:mtext>del total</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,12</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Encontrar el total</strong></p>
            <p>Si una tercera parte vale <m:math><m:mn>0,12</m:mn></m:math> kg, entonces el total corresponde a <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math> veces esa cantidad.</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>0,12</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,36</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Verificar el resultado</strong></p>
            <p>Comprobamos que la tercera parte de <m:math><m:mn>0,36</m:mn></m:math> es efectivamente <m:math><m:mn>0,12</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>0,36</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0,12</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>La condición del problema se cumple exactamente.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>Se necesitan en total <m:math><m:mn>0,36</m:mn></m:math> kg de azúcar.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>ChoiceB</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>